# Terraform variable files (contain OCIDs that we don't expose on this public repo).
# Use terraform.tfvars.example as a template; copy it to terraform.tfvars and fill in values.
# In CI/CD, values are injected via GitHub Variables instead.
terraform/terraform.tfvars
terraform/*.auto.tfvars
terraform/*.auto.tfvars.json

